snippet.title: Hot Pot Panic Trailer
snippet.description:
Cook, eat, converse! A game about eating hot pot and awkward conversations. Get it here: https://keanerie.itch.io/hot-pot-panic

Developed by Keane Ng (@keanerie) and featuring music and sound by Michael Berto (Paws Menu). Trailer by Sean Fagan.
